      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document defines a new Diameter application and associated Command Codes.  The Capabilities Update application is intended to allow the dynamic update of certain Diameter peer capabilities while the peer-to-peer connection is in the open state. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
